The,BitTrust,API,provides,a,common,platform,for,developers,of,applications,to,build,their,user,interfaces,around,It,removes,the,necessity,to,build,out,many,specific,features,for,every,application,and,instead,share,one,data,center,via,the,central,API,Applications,using,the,BitTrust,API,let,users,conduct,transactions,using,BitCoin,a,decentralized,internet,currency,The,BitTrust,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON